        <summary>ShareMouse lets you share your mouse and keyboard with multiple networked computers.</summary>
        <description>ShareMouse allows you to control any Mac or Windows PC with the mouse/keyboard of any other computer. To control a specific computer, move the mouse into the direction of the corresponding display. Once the mouse pointer reaches the border of a monitor, it jumps to the neighboring monitor and Sharemouse steps in to control the remote computer.</description>
